item.dc:creator: @Mental_Piracy Mental Piracy
item.description:
@Mental_Piracy wrote:

I assume you are using delta, it happens when the server is SUPPOSED to remove an npc, but in actuality moves it to coords 0 0. Restarting server or adding an npcreset command that INCLUDES jad will fix the problem, or hey you could just make it remove the npc instead of switching its location.
